	<li id="menu-item-17261" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-17261"><a href="https://uscnpm.org/trilateral-research-series/">Trilateral Research Series</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li id="menu-item-50161" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category current-post-ancestor current-menu-parent current-post-parent menu-item-50161"><a href="https://uscnpm.org/category/blog/">Blog</a></li>
